    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This Porsche 911 Carrera 2 features a high-revving M96 3.4L flat-six engine paired with a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical highlights include a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently serviced cooling system with an updated water pump and low-temp thermostat. The suspension geometry is dialed in with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, maintaining the legendary communicative feedback of the hydraulic steering rack. Power delivery is exceptionally linear through the Variocam range, and the braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers with significant rotor life remaining. A mechanically robust example optimized for the purist driver.",
