      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips consistent with responsible road use. The alloy wheels are crisp and free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium leather seats remain supple without any cracks or bolster wear, and the original carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every technological feature, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the multi-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, including a recent comprehensive service where all fluids were flushed and the brake pads were replaced. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a clean title and a complete binder of service records included for your peace of mind.",
